title: [Misun's Outfitting]
description: Beneath a domed white stucco ceiling, a multihued Vornavian silk tapestry hangs on one of the refined oak-paneled walls.  A heavy wooden desk and a brass treasure chest sit in opposite corners while a thick off-white carpet rests on a varnished dark oak floor.

Beneath a domed white stucco ceiling, a multihued Vornavian silk tapestry hangs on one of the refined oak-paneled walls.  A Vornavian silk-lined display case and a long brass clothing rack sit in opposite corners while an elegantly dressed maiden statue rests on a varnished dark oak floor.
